      "content": "it's not just about the degree though. it's like everything is just so heavy. waking up feels like a chore, and every single day is just more of the same struggle. i feel like im just taking up space. like, if i just disappeared, the world would keep spinning and nothing would actually be lost. i just want to find some kind of peace that isn't this constant, crushing weight.",
