    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't want to just 'accept' the weight anymore. i'm too tired to carry it. every time i think about trying again, i just feel this massive emptiness. it feels like the only way to actually get that peace i'm looking for is to just... stop everything. to really, finally rest. does that even make sense? like, is it wrong to just want the struggle to be over for good?",
